      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver residuals monitored; convergence tolerance set to 1e-6 for all load steps.",
      "rationale": "Static implicit solver with force residual tolerance of 1e-6 used throughout. No convergence failures observed across all 11 simulation runs. Numerical solver error is negligible."
