      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation inputs reviewed by a second qualified analyst; boundary conditions documented in a simulation plan.",
      "rationale": "A simulation plan was prepared prior to execution and independently reviewed. Boundary condition application (fixed lower block, displacement-controlled upper block per F1717) was confirmed by peer review. No use errors identified."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
