      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form assumptions (linear elasticity, frictional contact, geometric fidelity) are justified by literature and sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "Linear isotropic elasticity is appropriate for the pre-yield regime. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) at screw-rod and rod-block interfaces was validated against published sensitivity data. Geometric fidelity confirmed by CAD-to-FEA dimensional audit. Model form is adequate."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
