    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is documented and partially mitigated by the high fidelity of the single condition tested and the strong output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96). Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending.",
